                        Property specifying the class name of the SAX
                        XML parser to use.
                    </entry>
                    <entry>-</entry>
                    <entry>-</entry>
                    <entry>-</entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>org.exolab.castor.parser.validation</entry>
                    <entry>
                        Specifies whether to perform XML document
                        validation by default.
                    </entry>
                    <entry>
